{"tid":380452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖南婦燒衣祭病逝兒　倒酒精助燃搶火　5歲孫嚴重燒傷","createTime":"2017-08-30T06:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T06:55:05.000Z","uid":136994,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2239071fb232bafdda6fba5585f33840a68e69f5","tid":380452,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170829/s00004/1503990938844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170829%2Fs00004%2F1503990938844&d=hOj2yrHBh8ifRT3WMHuv3DQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=9276cd85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170829%2Fs00004%2F1503990938844&h=d78fc682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170829/s00004/1503990938844</a><br />\n<br />\n湖南一名5歲男童，其父不久前因癌症病逝，祖母日前帶他燒紙錢拜祭父親時，因難以點着紙錢而加酒精助燃，結果冒出大火令男童全身40%嚴重燒傷，估計要接受最少1個半月治療，醫療費料起碼要10多萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n5歲的賀語辰居於湖南常德市，其伯父和父親已相繼因鼻咽癌病逝，母親則在外打工養家。語辰的祖母上周六（26日）傍晚6時許，趁着農曆七月，帶語辰按習俗燒紙錢拜祭父親。她憶述當時將紙錢放於稻草上點燃，但點了幾次都只有火星，「我就放點酒精燃料進去發火，真的只有一點點」，結果冒出大火直撲往語辰身上。祖母連忙為孫兒撲火，之後送到附近的衛生院。<br />\n<br />\n由於語辰傷勢太重，衛生院為他簡單治理後即轉送到燒傷整形醫院治療。醫院主診醫生表示，語辰送到醫院時已休克，全身燒傷面積達40%，集中在頭面頸、雙上肢、軀幹等部位，「都是特重度燒傷」。雖然搶救20多小時後，語辰的呼吸循環已趨平穩，其精神狀態亦稍有好轉，但醫生指他「因大部分創面較深，需要多次麻醉手術才能完全封閉，治療需要一個半月左右，醫療費起碼要10多萬（人民幣）」。<br />\n<br />\n喺火入面倒酒精，真係得腦生喺屎忽嘅人先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe62b4e8aa716527213e4e1635abd91f1fc8641c","tid":380452,"uid":42767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"活人祭"},{"pid":"d8200e24c4293c344e6ca85d8011639dd94284a1","tid":380452,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"父親顯靈呀"},{"pid":"bf960e22d8c52dd22f2ebed42310c62dd76b7a9e","tid":380452,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f56f5d2bc0b2aefdd6354543bdec5c968eef74d","tid":380452,"uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"中國人的智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a529767268562ce154398c8d926bbe3a33c22b","tid":380452,"uid":3936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"燒個仔落去陪佢"},{"pid":"ebedb9e8586c7d2bdae183b45965abcfb96c7f86","tid":380452,"uid":22989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"陷家一齊落去"},{"pid":"6ceca8548e9068dde47df16e55470b9a6c9b77dd","tid":380452,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"一家團聚"},{"pid":"c5e405bb8792535a08f4ce9f1e12090562dcaf8b","tid":380452,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"咁就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab39c0bd88f743779add501613e263a4239690a","tid":380452,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"下次應該倒白電油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}